# Vocabulary

curated by the members of the english course for ROB and BGIP at TUBAF

- vocab for roboticists

## Vocab for geophysicists

    {{0}}
>Structure of the earth ([custom LiaScript](https://liascript.github.io/LiveEditor/?))

- crust
- upper / lower mantle
- outer / inner clojure
- Lithosphere / Asthenosphere / Mesosphere

    {{1}}
>volcanic / tectonic activities

plate tectonic

- continental drift
- divergent plates (mid-oceanic ridge)
- convergent plates (subduction & orogenesis / orogeny)
- transform plates (San Andreas fault)

different kinds of volcanic activities

- plate boundaries
- intraplate activity (hot spot vulcanism, some caused by tectonic activities -> subduction)

Various stages of tectonic activity associated with the Dongwu movement (DM) and the associated sedimentary responses in the Sichuan Basin, Southwest China:
